ides</strong> and <strong>Microsoft HoloLens</strong>.</p>\n\n<p/><strong>Smart Factory Mixed Reality Champion Badge issued to:</strong></p>\n\n<table style=\"width:100%\">\n  <tr>\n    <td>Name</td>\n    <td>@{triggerOutputs()?['body/ur_firstname']} @{triggerOutputs()?['body/ur_lastname']}</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Email</td>\n    <td>@{triggerOutputs()?['body/ur_email']}</td>\n  </tr>\n    <tr>\n    <td>Issed on</td>\n    <td>@{triggerOutputs()?['body/ur_mrcompetencyearned']}</td>\n  </tr>\n    <tr>\n    <td>Issued by</td>\n    <td><a href=\"https://www.sipbb.ch/en/forschung/swiss-smart-factory/\">Swiss Smart Factory</a></td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<p>Enclose we share with you, your <strong>Smart Factory Mixed Reality Champion Badge</strong>.</p>\n<br>\n<img src=\"https://ssfdyncfsp2d870830e53a.blob.core.windows.net/images/SwissSmartFactoryMixedRealityCampionBadge.png\" alt=\"Swiss Smart Factory Mixed Reality Campion Badge\" width=\"500\" height=\"400\">\n\n<br>\n<p>We hope you enjoyed your <a href=\"https://www.sipbb.ch/en/forschung/swiss-smart-factory/\"><strong>Swiss Smart Factory</strong></a>&nbsp;visit and were able to delight you with our Mixed Reality experience demo.</p>\n\n<p>Shared you earned Smart Factory Mixed Reality Champion Badge and comment your experiences on <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/\"><strong>LinkedIn</strong></a>&nbsp;profile.</p>\n\n<p>Regards<br>\nYour Swiss Smart Factory team</p>\n\n</body>"},"authentication":"@parameters('$authentication')"}}}}},"schemaVersion":"1.0.0.0"}